{
  "stem": "1033.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It all seemed mysterious to me then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at this point, I just think, quaint.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But there are so many riddles when a person is a child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think more or less all of us start that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I visited my mother in the hospital once.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I recall the sisters showed her from behind a window.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she looked at me, and she was very thin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said to the nurse, to the sister, see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's my big boy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I just looked at her, and I had a deep pain in my heart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- I couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a feeling, you must have had to live it to know what it is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't wish it on anyone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in a way, it had left a lot of stuff inside me built up, which somehow or other had to be resolved.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I attribute my way of looking at the world to the kind of very early challenges that I had to deal with and-- and get beyond.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Many of my dreams were running and being afraid, and especially being afraid of God, and knowing that I had done the wrong thing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had said, God, God, God, many times, and he's going to strike me dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and unfortunately, there was no one I could talk about this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I was-- when I was four years old, the shochet who came twice a week to kill the animals, that they would be kosher, started teaching me Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, that was bizarre.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to wear my tzitzits, and that was uncomfortable because it used to slide into places where it didn't feel right.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I was terrified from my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My grandfather, on the other hand, had six daughters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He desperately wanted a son.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- they tried often enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was the first grandson.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You can imagine the weight of all his zeal fell on me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But at the time, I didn't understand that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a tight situation, and I willingly escaped it as often as I could to my aunt Rosi, who lived in [NON-ENGLISH], about seven kilometers from the village where my grandparents lived.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there, I was much more free, and they had a-- she and her husband, Uncle Imre Frank, had a-- a hardware store, but they also sold candy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there I-- it was a different world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were-- I didn't have to wear my tzitzits.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and I made friends in that village, too, with another boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were good times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I still think of them fondly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The orphanage was a Jewish institution, it was-- I guess the [NON-ENGLISH], which means the Foundation of the Israelites of Budapest, or the Jewish Orphanage-- the Founded Jewish Orphanage of the Israelites of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some very famous people, incidentally, had grown up in this place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was in-- it was in a-- functioning since the very early 1900s.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when I got there, it had practically 40 years of operation, or perhaps even more.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the morning, we had to get washed, dressed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to go to prayer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The children were from the age of five to about 20.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were four public schools in the orphanage itself, where other kids came in, not just the orphans from the area.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I missed that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then there was the middle school kids, and I belonged to these groups.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were grouped-- we were in four groups.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The little ones, who were up to grade four, the middle kids, who were up to, say, grade eight, and then the people who were trained for some sort of trade, and very few who were allowed to go to higher education-- who were very well-- who distinguished themselves as good students.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there were half a dozen of those.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had a room to ourselves, the various age groups.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the various age groups had different teachers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was [NON-ENGLISH], who was looking after the little ones, who incidentally is living in Toronto-- married one of the older boys, who became a-- a radiologist, who just retired, by the name of Pater-- Dr.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Pater.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was my group, and I had a teacher called Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Wolfe, who was only eight years older than I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it seemed to me like, at the time, he was much older.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was another group, who was looked after by Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Leibowitz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The director's name was Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Lederer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was a wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
